  "detailed_description": "Mia Faircroft goes on a new Hidden Object quest! When an old friend calls for her help with restoring a cathedral, Mia packs her bags for the seaside town of Porto Nacosti, Italy! Explore lavishly illustrated and animated locations.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721690/extras/00f23cb4ec1e24ca8201eb24e13b6590.poster.avif?t=1729156784\" width=600 height=372 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721690/extras/00f23cb4ec1e24ca8201eb24e13b6590.webm?t=1729156784\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721690/extras/00f23cb4ec1e24ca8201eb24e13b6590.mp4?t=1729156784\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Play over 30 fun minigames, each centered on a piece of art!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721690/extras/d77c2fba5468ed4d7ff90f5a6af89fbe.poster.avif?t=1729156784\" width=600 height=372 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721690/extras/d77c2fba5468ed4d7ff90f5a6af89fbe.webm?t=1729156784\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721690/extras/d77c2fba5468ed4d7ff90f5a6af89fbe.mp4?t=1729156784\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Escape to the summer seaside haven of Porto Nacosti!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721690/extras/aa76370892c898feb9af30e072efdfbc.poster.avif?t=1729156784\" width=600 height=372 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721690/extras